---
import BaseHead from '@/components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Privacy Policy — Alex Morcillo" description="Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit this website." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
			<p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ink-muted dark:text-cream-muted mb-6 animate-fade-up">
				Legal
			</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent my-8 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s"></div>

			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
				<h2>Introduction</h2>
				<p>
					At <a href="https://alexmorcillo.com">Alex Morcillo</a>, we are mindful of the needs of internet users and aware of the importance of rigorously protecting the personal information entrusted to us. We include this privacy statement so that you are aware of our policy regarding the processing of personal data obtained from our visitors and users.
				</p>
				<p>
					As a user, you accept these terms by the mere act of reading, viewing, or browsing this website. If you do not accept them, you must leave the site without making any use of it or its content and without accessing any linked pages.
				</p>

				<h2>Data Controller</h2>
				<p>
					The owner of this website and the party responsible for data processing is Alejandro Morcillo Montejo. You may contact us through:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@alexmorcillo.com">contact@alexmorcillo.com</a></li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
				<p>
					Our website includes specific sections where you can enter your data to receive information about updates to our website and about some of the programs we distribute. We assure you that the information you provide will be handled in a strictly confidential manner.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Contact form:</strong> To maintain contact with you or carry out other required actions.
				</p>
				<p>
					Your data will be stored for as long as there is a foreseeable use for the purpose for which it was collected.
				</p>
				<p>
					No automated decision-making is performed with your data.
				</p>
				<p>
					This website may use cookies. Please refer to our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>.
				</p>

				<h2>Legal Basis for Data Processing</h2>
				<p>
					Your data is used because you have given us your consent to use the information you provide through our forms for the specific purpose indicated in each one. Your data is only necessary for the particular uses for which it is requested; if you choose not to provide it, those services will not be available.
				</p>

				<h2>Data Transfers and Disclosures</h2>
				<p>
					We make a firm commitment that the data you provide to Alejandro Morcillo Montejo will not be sold or transferred to third parties without the prior consent of the data subject, under any concept or circumstance, except with express consent or legal obligation.
				</p>
				<p>
					Our website contains links to third-party websites. Alejandro Morcillo Montejo is not responsible for the privacy policies and practices of these other sites.
				</p>

				<h2>Rights of Data Subjects</h2>
				<p>
					You have the right to access the information about you stored in our databases, to rectify any errors, to have it deleted, to restrict its processing, to object to its processing, and to withdraw your consent if you so wish.
				</p>
				<p>
					To do so, simply send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@alexmorcillo.com">contact@alexmorcillo.com</a>, where we will be happy to assist you with any inquiry, comment, or clarification you may need.
				</p>
				<p>
					For further information on related matters, the reference site in Spain is the <strong>Spanish Data Protection Agency</strong> (Agencia Espa&ntilde;ola de Protecci&oacute;n de Datos), where you have the right to file a claim.
				</p>

				<p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-cream-muted">
					Last updated: March 2026
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
